import { Tabs } from 'antd'
import React from 'react'
import Icerikler from '../icerikler/Icerikler'
import RssIcerikler from '../rssIcerikler/Icerikler'

export default function KategoriDetay() {
  return (
    <Tabs type="card">
    <Tabs.TabPane tab="جميع المحتوى" key="1">
        <Icerikler/>
    </Tabs.TabPane>
    <Tabs.TabPane tab="جميع المحتوى (RSS)" key="2">
        <RssIcerikler/>
    </Tabs.TabPane>
  </Tabs>
  )
}
